{"tid":874286,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"《機動戰士高達F91》主角聲優辻谷耕史突然去世 享年56歲","createTime":"2018-10-24T05:44:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-25T13:45:35.000Z","uid":49391,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"379cdb0a787fb9539d5f49ad17dfe241ac68ac41","tid":874286,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T05:44:49.000Z","msg":"根據日本媒體的報導，曾在《機動戰士高達F91》、《犬夜叉》等動畫中為重要角色配音的知名聲優辻谷耕史在10月17日因腦梗阻不幸去世，享年56歲。這也是非常的突然，辻谷耕史在10月14日還參加了與立木文彥組成樂隊的紀念直播，大家也是紛紛祝福辻谷耕史一路走好。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LxNUxaV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLxNUxaV.jpg&h=3371c2af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n辻谷耕史配過的代表性角色有《機動戰士高達F91》的男主角亞諾，《3&times;3 Eyes》的藤井八雲，《犬夜叉》中的彌勒，《灌籃高手》的藤真健司、《 Fate/stay night》的遠坂時臣等等大家熟知的角色。除了配音的工作外，辻谷耕史還在進入21世紀後開始出任動畫的音響監督，辻谷耕史參與配音的《學園BASRAR》與擔任音響監督的《錢進球場》第二季動畫正在播出當中，他的突然離世也是讓人唏噓不已。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DcASiQ2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDcASiQ2.jpg&h=7b3b1497&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MsX5DQ2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMsX5DQ2.jpg&h=f2194e7b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d1ea76aac3667533a7dea0c6634471cce4559efd","tid":874286,"uid":49391,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T05:46:48.000Z","msg":"等到死左都唔動畫化海盜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nFUCK U 啦笨大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"696fed389bdbcb6bd31086255a543f6c3022849c","tid":874286,"uid":3559,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T05:49:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"> 爛佗！！！！！</span></span>"},{"pid":"ff038bfe4ab1534d0d8b20161165625b3d8c6c4a","tid":874286,"uid":45318,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T05:57:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">